1
00:01:28,240 --> 00:01:30,920
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL
"MY QUEEN" BY XIE LOUNAN

2
00:01:43,360 --> 00:01:44,520
Miss Ling.

3
00:01:45,720 --> 00:01:47,000
Greetings, Miss Ling.

4
00:01:47,080 --> 00:01:48,560
I've gathered all members of
Fenglai Pavilion from every region.

5
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:49,480
They've been slipping
into the Capital in secret

6
00:01:49,560 --> 00:01:50,400
and are now standing by.

7
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:51,880
Very well. Follow the plan.

8
00:01:51,960 --> 00:01:53,560
Take your men to the Prince of
Yuzhang's Manor and assist Zhong Lin.

9
00:01:53,640 --> 00:01:55,680
The rest is to stay put for now.

10
00:01:55,760 --> 00:01:56,840
Yes.

11
00:01:56,920 --> 00:01:58,400
What about you, Miss Ling?

12
00:01:59,480 --> 00:02:00,520
Phoenix Terrace.

13
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:39,160
Minister Lin, you're back.

14
00:02:39,760 --> 00:02:40,840
Your Majesty,

15
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:42,440
I have returned

16
00:02:43,120 --> 00:02:44,400
alive.

17
00:02:45,880 --> 00:02:48,560
You've served two reigns
and are revered by all.

18
00:02:49,560 --> 00:02:50,920
Yet due to the Ling faction's framing,

19
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:51,920
you rose and fell three times

20
00:02:52,520 --> 00:02:54,480
and were only reinstated today.

21
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:55,840
You've suffered a lot.

22
00:02:55,920 --> 00:02:58,760
I was stubborn and rigid.

23
00:02:59,480 --> 00:03:02,000
Your Majesty's decision to exile me

24
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:04,240
was to protect me.

25
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:06,960
I understand.

26
00:03:08,440 --> 00:03:10,400
Minister Lin, you're an upright man.

27
00:03:10,480 --> 00:03:13,440
The future of Great Qi will depend on you.

28
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:18,480
Greetings, Your Majesty.

29
00:03:21,480 --> 00:03:22,560
Mr. Li.

30
00:03:23,520 --> 00:03:24,720
I hope you will continue

31
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:27,560
to select worthy talents for Great Qi

32
00:03:27,640 --> 00:03:29,480
and demand justice for the people.

33
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:32,520
Also, the status verification
system must be abolished.

34
00:03:32,600 --> 00:03:35,440
Only then can
Great Qi remain stable for long.

35
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:38,160
Your Majesty, if you face any difficulty,

36
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:40,280
you must tell us.

37
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:42,920
Even if it costs my life,

38
00:03:43,520 --> 00:03:46,320
I will protect you.

39
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:49,720
I appreciate it, Mr. Li.

40
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:51,200
I would give

41
00:03:51,720 --> 00:03:54,280
everything for Great Qi,

42
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:55,960
even if at the cost of my life.

43
00:04:30,520 --> 00:04:33,360
Since birth,
I have suffered from cold sickness.

44
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:36,120
It's only with everyone's care

45
00:04:36,200 --> 00:04:37,320
that I have lived to see this day.

46
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:40,360
I thank you all.

47
00:04:41,400 --> 00:04:43,760
Thank you for never abandoning me

48
00:04:43,840 --> 00:04:45,920
so that we could build
this flourishing age together.

49
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:47,920
Today,

50
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:50,560
I'd like to look upon

51
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:53,000
my capital,

52
00:04:53,520 --> 00:04:54,920
my officials and people,

53
00:04:55,440 --> 00:04:56,680
and my land.

54
00:05:01,760 --> 00:05:04,000
Long live the wise ruler!

55
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:49,520
Golden Phoenix Bids Farewell.

56
00:05:50,640 --> 00:05:51,720
<i>Cangcang,</i>

57
00:05:53,400 --> 00:05:54,840
<i>when you see these fireworks,</i>

58
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:56,840
<i>leave this place.</i>

59
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:57,920
<i>Don't come back.</i>

60
00:05:58,440 --> 00:06:00,240
<i>This place is dangerous.</i>

61
00:06:02,280 --> 00:06:03,720
<i>If I survive this,</i>

62
00:06:05,200 --> 00:06:06,800
<i>I will never let you leave me again.</i>

63
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:15,200
Could it be…?

64
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:18,200
Xiao Huan!

65
00:06:46,920 --> 00:06:47,960
Your Majesty,

66
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:50,840
you said you wished to die with dignity.

67
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:55,160
Do it now.

68
00:07:26,440 --> 00:07:29,760
Is this the ending you all wanted?

69
00:07:47,840 --> 00:07:49,840
- Your Majesty!
- Your Majesty!

70
00:07:51,400 --> 00:07:53,920
