00:07:59,880 --> 00:08:01,200
Xiao Huan!

73
00:08:06,160 --> 00:08:12,040
- Your Majesty!
- Your Majesty!

74
00:08:44,520 --> 00:08:45,720
No!

75
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:48,320
Cangcang.

76
00:08:49,680 --> 00:08:51,320
Zhong Lin. Where's Xiao Huan?

77
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:53,520
His Majesty jumped from Phoenix Terrace.

78
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:54,920
The river was fast.

79
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:56,760
Shi Yan and I have searched for him.

80
00:08:56,840 --> 00:08:58,680
Xiao Qianqing's men are
also looking along the banks,

81
00:08:58,760 --> 00:09:00,200
