82
00:09:04,640 --> 00:09:06,160
Cangcang. Where are you going, Cangcang?

83
00:09:06,240 --> 00:09:07,080
I'm going to find him.

84
00:09:07,160 --> 00:09:09,080
Du Tingxin has
soldiers all over Phoenix Terrace.

85
00:09:09,160 --> 00:09:11,200
If you go now,
you're walking to your death.

86
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:27,040
Saintess.

87
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:28,320
Speak.

88
00:09:28,400 --> 00:09:30,240
The Emperor of Great Qi
jumped from Phoenix Terrace.

89
00:09:42,240 --> 00:09:43,280
Is he dead?

90
00:09:43,880 --> 00:09:45,040
They haven't found his body.

91
00:09:45,120 --> 00:09:48,200
But no one has ever
survived the Qining River.

92
00:09:54,160 --> 00:09:55,840
He does have some backbone

93
00:09:56,640 --> 00:09:59,480
