97
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:11,400
WUYING HALL

98
00:10:14,200 --> 00:10:15,360
<i>Well?</i>

99
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:18,480
<i>Do you like the gift I gave you, Qianqing?</i>

100
00:10:18,560 --> 00:10:19,880
<i>No.</i>

101
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:22,040
<i>When I wanted it, you didn't give it.</i>

102
00:10:22,120 --> 00:10:23,680
<i>It means nothing when it comes late.</i>

103
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:25,840
It's like sincerity.

104
00:10:26,400 --> 00:10:27,400
If no one answers it,

105
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:29,800
then the answer no longer matters.

106
00:10:31,200 --> 00:10:32,600
Tell me.

107
00:10:32,680 --> 00:10:35,280
Other than the map, what else do you want?

108
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:40,640
<i>I only wish to serve you</i>

109
00:10:40,720 --> 00:10:43,600
<i>and help you claim the throne.</i>

110
00:10:44,400 --> 00:10:45,600
Let's celebrate in advance.

111
00:10:45,680 --> 00:10:48,320
May Great Qi have peaceful weather

112
00:10:48,400 --> 00:10:50,360
and thriving people.

113
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:54,280
<i>Xiao Huan…</i>

114
00:10:57,600 --> 00:10:59,520
He jumped from Phoenix Terrace.

115
00:10:59,600 --> 00:11:00,560
He might…

116
00:11:00,640 --> 00:11:02,320
- He might be…
- I don't believe it.

117
00:11:03,800 --> 00:11:05,840
I don't believe a single word you say

118
00:11:06,480 --> 00:11:07,560
unless I see it myself.

119
00:11:07,640 --> 00:11:09,480
