<i>unless we removed the pith.</i>

127
00:11:43,840 --> 00:11:46,160
<i>But you didn't like the ones I peeled.</i>

128
00:11:46,920 --> 00:11:48,080
<i>You said they were ugly.</i>

129
00:11:48,680 --> 00:11:50,240
<i>You would only eat</i>
<i>the ones Xiao Huan peeled.</i>

130
00:11:53,360 --> 00:11:55,000
<i>I was upset</i>

131
00:11:56,880 --> 00:12:00,280
- <i>so I peeled a lot for you.</i>
- Tasty. I want more.

132
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:02,880
