133
00:12:04,880 --> 00:12:06,640
If you like it, I can peel more.

134
00:12:11,880 --> 00:12:12,920
Here.

135
00:12:13,520 --> 00:12:14,960
No. Ugly.

136
00:12:19,280 --> 00:12:21,320
Ying, you must finish the mandarins

137
00:12:21,400 --> 00:12:22,320
I peeled for you.

138
00:12:22,400 --> 00:12:25,160
If not, I'll tell our mother
that you're playing favorites.

139
00:12:25,240 --> 00:12:27,360
Your mandarins are ugly.
I don't want them.

140
00:12:27,440 --> 00:12:29,120
Eat.

141
00:12:29,200 --> 00:12:31,320
- If you don't finish them…
- No. Your mandarins are ugly.

142
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:34,080
Eat.

143
00:12:35,200 --> 00:12:36,440
You have to finish them.

144
00:12:38,400 --> 00:12:39,320
Ying.

145
00:12:39,400 --> 00:12:40,880
<i>Huan.</i>

146
00:12:41,880 --> 00:12:44,920
Help, Huan.

147
00:12:47,480 --> 00:12:48,480
Ying!

148
00:12:49,440 --> 00:12:50,400
Ying!

149
00:12:52,160 --> 00:12:53,200
Ying!

150
00:13:05,240 --> 00:13:06,240
You're bad!

151
00:13:06,320 --> 00:13:07,520
Ying.

152
00:13:07,600 --> 00:13:10,040
You're bad! I don't want them. Go away!

153
00:13:10,120 --> 00:13:11,520
- Ying.
- You're bad!

154
00:13:11,600 --> 00:13:13,320
- Ying.
- You're bad!

155
00:13:13,400 --> 00:13:14,600
You're bad!

156
00:13:14,680 --> 00:13:16,120
Don't be afraid, Ying.

157
00:13:16,200 --> 00:13:17,360
I'm here.

158
00:13:17,440 --> 00:13:18,680
Don't be afraid, Ying.

159
00:13:25,400 --> 00:13:26,480
Huan.

160
00:13:28,120 --> 00:13:29,480
What exactly happened

161
00:13:29,560 --> 00:13:30,800
during the fire at Luling Palace that day?

162
00:13:31,760 --> 00:13:32,920
What do you think happened?

163
00:13:34,640 --> 00:13:35,640
Why did you abandon Ying?

164
00:13:36,600 --> 00:13:38,280
You knew how she loved you, respected you.

165
00:13:38,360 --> 00:13:39,720
Why didn't you save her?

166
00:13:46,040 --> 00:13:48,600
You and I
were born into the imperial family.

167
00:13:49,280 --> 00:13:50,280
Yes.

168
00:13:50,800 --> 00:13:52,800
We were born into the imperial family.

169
00:13:54,240 --> 00:13:55,480
<i>Is this</i>

170
00:13:56,280 --> 00:13:57,400
<i>the ending you all wanted?</i>

171
00:14:00,600 --> 00:14:02,880
<i>What did Du Tingxin do to you?</i>

172
00:14:05,520 --> 00:14:06,760
Xiao Huan.

173
00:14:10,000 --> 00:14:13,240
Why did you choose to
jump from Phoenix Terrace?

174
00:14:14,760 --> 00:14:17,560
You haven't even told me the truth.

175
00:14:22,360 --> 00:14:24,360
What should I do now?

176
00:14:28,400 --> 00:14:31,000
VIRTUE HELD WITHIN

177
00:14:31,080 --> 00:14:31,960
Your Highness,

178
00:14:32,040 --> 00:14:33,320
the Imperial Preceptor ordered
me to bring the Princess of Ding'an back.

179
00:15:20,680 --> 00:15:21,960
Where's Cangcang?

180
00:15:24,440 --> 00:15:25,960
Even like this,

181
00:15:26,560 --> 00:15:29,800
- all you care about…
- Tell me where Ling Cangcang is!

182
00:15:37,560 --> 00:15:38,600
She's fine.

183
00:15:39,200 --> 00:15:40,880
She's the Empress of Great Qi.

184
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:43,160
Of course, she's in Linghe Hall.

185
00:16:14,280 --> 00:16:15,200
Your Majesty,

186
00:16:15,720 --> 00:16:16,600
it's been a long while.

187
00:16:18,960 --> 00:16:20,800
It feels like a lifetime.

188
00:16:21,480 --> 00:16:23,480
Preceptor Du, you went to all this trouble

189
00:16:23,560 --> 00:16:24,960
to bring me back to Linghe Hall.

190
00:16:25,720 --> 00:16:27,040
Surely it's not for a casual chat.

191
00:16:28,480 --> 00:16:30,080
You're the Empress.

192
00:16:30,160 --> 00:16:31,800
Naturally, you should be in Linghe Hall.

193
00:16:32,720 --> 00:16:34,640
I'm only doing my
duty as Imperial Preceptor

194
00:16:35,280 --> 00:16:37,240
to escort Your Majesty back to the palace.

195
00:16:39,480 --> 00:16:41,400
- You want to kill me?
- Of course.

196
00:16:46,480 --> 00:16:49,560
I can't wait to cut you into pieces.

197
00:16:50,280 --> 00:16:51,360
If not for you,

198
00:16:51,440 --> 00:16:54,280
Xiao Huan wouldn't
have ended up like this.

199
00:16:54,960 --> 00:16:58,720
His condition today is all thanks to you.

200
00:17:02,960 --> 00:17:05,480
Your fate is said to curse His Majesty.

201
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:07,640
As long as you're near him,

202
00:17:07,720 --> 00:17:09,720
he will never meet a good end.

203
00:17:09,800 --> 00:17:11,280
He's not dead.

204
00:17:12,839 --> 00:17:13,800
He can't be dead.

205
00:17:13,880 --> 00:17:16,079
I saw him jump from
Phoenix Terrace with my own eyes.

206
00:17:16,680 --> 00:17:17,880
Even if you lie to yourself,

207
00:17:18,480 --> 00:17:20,839
I'm telling you, he will not survive.

208
00:17:24,040 --> 00:17:25,319
For you,

209
00:17:25,400 --> 00:17:27,119
Xiao Huan gave up
the only medicine that could save him.

210
00:17:27,200 --> 00:17:28,560
What were you doing?

211
00:17:29,320 --> 00:17:30,520
For you,

212
00:17:30,600 --> 00:17:32,600
he risked his life to travel
alone to Xijiang for peace negotiations.

213
00:17:32,680 --> 00:17:33,920
What were you doing?

214
00:17:34,560 --> 00:17:35,880
Ling Cangcang,

215
00:17:36,480 --> 00:17:38,040
he gave you everything he could.

216
00:17:38,760 --> 00:17:40,240
Now that he's already
jumped from Phoenix Terrace.

217
00:17:40,320 --> 00:17:41,360
Why are you still alive?

218
00:17:42,320 --> 00:17:43,560
Why didn't you

219
00:17:44,360 --> 00:17:46,800
die with him?

220
00:17:55,440 --> 00:17:56,560
Madam.

221
00:18:02,280 --> 00:18:03,120
Madam.

222
00:18:12,120 --> 00:18:15,400
They found this
blood-soaked robe in the Qining River.

223
00:18:43,480 --> 00:18:44,600
How could I…

224
00:18:46,520 --> 00:18:49,200
How could I possibly

225
00:18:50,320 --> 00:18:51,520
let you die so easily?

226
00:19:15,480 --> 00:19:16,680
Don't worry.

227
00:19:17,760 --> 00:19:19,680
I won't torment you for long.

228
00:19:20,680 --> 00:19:22,040
Once I've had my fun,

229
00:19:22,920 --> 00:19:24,600
I'll send you

230
00:19:26,160 --> 00:19:27,680
to your demise.

231
00:19:29,560 --> 00:19:30,680
Du Tingxin,

232
00:19:32,600 --> 00:19:34,000
if you want to kill me,

233
00:19:34,920 --> 00:19:36,480
do it now.

234
00:19:37,720 --> 00:19:38,800
Otherwise,

235
00:19:40,800 --> 00:19:43,200
I swear I'll make you pay.

236
00:19:45,640 --> 00:19:46,760
As matters stand,

237
00:19:48,480 --> 00:19:50,560
what price could you make me pay?

238
00:22:01,480 --> 00:22:04,200
It's been three days since
His Majesty fell into the river.

239
00:22:04,280 --> 00:22:05,880
The Capital Patrol Office
has been dispatched

240
00:22:05,960 --> 00:22:08,160
and searched the entire Qining River,

241
00:22:08,240 --> 00:22:10,960
but they've found no trace of him.

242
00:22:12,880 --> 00:22:13,920
Your Highness,

243
00:22:14,520 --> 00:22:16,160
the Qining River is dangerous.

244
00:22:16,840 --> 00:22:19,280
