undercurrents and whirlpools.

245
00:22:19,360 --> 00:22:20,800
I fear His Majesty

246
00:22:20,880 --> 00:22:22,560
may not survive.

247
00:22:22,640 --> 00:22:23,720
- Yes.
- Yes.

248
00:22:25,080 --> 00:22:27,200
The nation can't be
without a ruler for even a day.

249
00:22:27,800 --> 00:22:30,680
