263
00:23:12,640 --> 00:23:13,760
What will become of the imperial court?

264
00:23:14,400 --> 00:23:15,600
In my opinion,

265
00:23:16,200 --> 00:23:17,440
at a time like this,

266
00:23:17,520 --> 00:23:19,120
only the Prince of Yuzhang…

267
00:23:19,200 --> 00:23:21,120
I'm not interested.

268
00:23:23,280 --> 00:23:24,160
Prince of Yuzhang.

269
00:23:25,240 --> 00:23:26,280
If any of you

270
00:23:27,000 --> 00:23:29,480
