00:23:43,080 --> 00:23:44,560
and fell into
the river from Phoenix Terrace.

274
00:23:45,240 --> 00:23:47,920
All the ministers present
saw it with your own eyes.

275
00:23:48,760 --> 00:23:50,560
No one who falls into the Qining River

276
00:23:50,640 --> 00:23:52,680
has ever survived.

277
00:23:52,760 --> 00:23:56,040
Even though the Capital atrol Office
is still searching…

278
00:23:56,120 --> 00:23:57,000
Whether alive or dead,

279
00:23:57,600 --> 00:23:58,760
we must find His Majesty.

280
00:23:59,720 --> 00:24:01,720
Until it's confirmed,

281
00:24:01,800 --> 00:24:03,240
no one

282
00:24:04,080 --> 00:24:05,360
is to covet the throne.

283
00:24:07,880 --> 00:24:09,240
Minister Lin,

284
00:24:09,320 --> 00:24:10,760
I know you're loyal to the Emperor.

285
00:24:11,440 --> 00:24:13,760
I myself have known
His Majesty since childhood.

286
00:24:14,560 --> 00:24:16,120
All the more reason
I can't accept this either.

287
00:24:19,000 --> 00:24:20,800
But if His Majesty can't be found,

288
00:24:21,560 --> 00:24:23,440
we can't wait forever.

289
00:24:24,840 --> 00:24:27,240
You're right, Preceptor Du.

290
00:24:27,320 --> 00:24:29,000
- True.
- Yes.

291
00:24:32,640 --> 00:24:35,720
However, according to
the founding laws of Great Qi,

292
00:24:35,800 --> 00:24:38,080
if the emperor's life or
death remains unknown,

293
00:24:38,160 --> 00:24:39,320
only after one hundred days

294
00:24:39,840 --> 00:24:43,600
with no word
may the throne pass to another.

295
00:24:43,680 --> 00:24:44,960
One hundred days?

296
00:24:45,920 --> 00:24:48,080
If any of you doubt it,

297
00:24:48,160 --> 00:24:49,440
you may consult the law

298
00:24:50,040 --> 00:24:53,040
and see whether I lie.

299
00:24:53,120 --> 00:24:54,160
Uh…

300
00:24:58,760 --> 00:25:01,080
Minister Lin has served two reigns

301
00:25:01,160 --> 00:25:04,120
and even helped
the late Emperor revise the code.

302
00:25:04,720 --> 00:25:05,720
He's never mistaken.

303
00:25:06,800 --> 00:25:09,560
However, during these one hundred days…

304
00:25:11,080 --> 00:25:12,200
We must ask the Prince of Yuzhang

305
00:25:12,800 --> 00:25:16,160
to act as Regent during this period.

306
00:25:16,240 --> 00:25:19,040
When His Majesty returns,
all will naturally return

307
00:25:19,640 --> 00:25:20,560
to its rightful order.

308
00:25:22,080 --> 00:25:23,200
Yes.

309
00:25:24,000 --> 00:25:25,760
That makes sense.

310
00:25:33,640 --> 00:25:34,960
Please stay, Prince of Yuzhang.

311
00:25:41,880 --> 00:25:44,360
His Majesty jumped from Phoenix Terrace,
and we don't know if he's alive.

312
00:25:45,320 --> 00:25:46,840
You don't seem to care.

313
00:25:48,880 --> 00:25:50,560
Why should I care about

314
00:25:50,640 --> 00:25:52,480
the murderer
who killed my mother and Ying?

315
00:25:53,720 --> 00:25:57,080
Do you have no interest in the throne?

316
00:25:59,600 --> 00:26:01,040
Since when have I ever cared for it?

317
00:26:02,160 --> 00:26:05,480
I only wanted the throne

318
00:26:06,080 --> 00:26:09,040
because Xiao Huan
valued it more than his own life.

319
00:26:10,480 --> 00:26:12,000
If he dies,

320
00:26:12,960 --> 00:26:15,440
what use is the throne to me?

321
00:26:17,960 --> 00:26:19,920
Right now I have only one thought.

322
00:26:20,520 --> 00:26:23,280
I hope he doesn't die in the Qining River.

323
00:26:23,360 --> 00:26:26,400
I want to take his life with my own hands.

324
00:26:27,840 --> 00:26:29,520
Then you should think about

325
00:26:30,400 --> 00:26:31,960
how to find His Majesty first.

326
00:26:33,880 --> 00:26:35,200
By the way,

327
00:26:35,280 --> 00:26:36,800
the Empress weeps day and night.

328
00:26:36,880 --> 00:26:38,600
She says she wants
to die with His Majesty.

329
00:26:39,200 --> 00:26:41,080
Your Highness,

330
00:26:41,160 --> 00:26:42,600
what do you think we should do with her?

331
00:26:45,000 --> 00:26:46,120
What do the rites say?

332
00:26:46,640 --> 00:26:48,960
If there is no news
from His Majesty after a hundred days,

333
00:26:49,040 --> 00:26:51,600
the Empress must be buried with him.

334
00:26:52,200 --> 00:26:53,200
We'll follow this rite then.

335
00:26:56,000 --> 00:26:56,920
I shall obey.

336
00:26:59,880 --> 00:27:00,920
Your Highness,

337
00:27:01,440 --> 00:27:06,160
when the decree announcing
the emperor's passing is issued,

338
00:27:06,240 --> 00:27:08,840
please deliver the decree

339
00:27:08,920 --> 00:27:10,200
for the Empress to be buried with him.

340
00:27:11,720 --> 00:27:13,680
I will.

341
00:27:16,440 --> 00:27:17,800
It was Xiao Huan.

342
00:27:18,400 --> 00:27:19,840
He fooled me.

343
00:27:20,800 --> 00:27:22,040
Now it's clear

344
00:27:22,800 --> 00:27:25,440
that he was the one who killed Ying.

345
00:27:25,520 --> 00:27:28,160
He would rather choose death
than admit it.

346
00:27:28,840 --> 00:27:30,440
So he can't blame me

347
00:27:31,000 --> 00:27:33,600
for destroying everything he cares about.

348
00:27:46,560 --> 00:27:47,400
Your Highness.

349
00:27:50,280 --> 00:27:52,080
Investigate all contact

350
00:27:52,160 --> 00:27:54,880
between Nanrong Palace and
Xuanguang Hall before the incident.

351
00:27:54,960 --> 00:27:56,240
Do it quietly.

352
00:27:56,320 --> 00:27:58,440
Don't let anyone in the palace find out.

353
00:27:58,520 --> 00:27:59,680
Yes, Your Highness.

354
00:28:07,480 --> 00:28:11,480
PROSPERITY IN FULL VIGOR

355
00:28:59,240 --> 00:29:00,400
Your Highness.

356
00:29:08,320 --> 00:29:13,280
LINGHE HALL

357
00:29:18,560 --> 00:29:19,720
Your Highness.

358
00:29:20,960 --> 00:29:21,880
The Imperial Preceptor said

359
00:29:22,560 --> 00:29:24,440
Her Majesty is grieving too deeply

360
00:29:24,520 --> 00:29:25,760
and shouldn't be disturbed.

361
00:29:25,840 --> 00:29:27,640
But she must repay me

362
00:29:28,160 --> 00:29:30,520
what she owes me.

363
00:30:11,960 --> 00:30:15,320
Now you finally understand my pain.

364
00:30:28,280 --> 00:30:29,440
Give it back to me.

365
00:30:33,720 --> 00:30:34,920
The pain of having your heart ripped out.

366
00:30:35,680 --> 00:30:37,040
The pain of a thousand
arrows through the chest.

367
00:30:39,760 --> 00:30:41,360
I want you

368
00:30:41,880 --> 00:30:43,240
to feel it just as I have.

369
00:30:47,600 --> 00:30:49,360
Soon,

370
00:30:49,440 --> 00:30:51,320
the news of His Majesty's passing

371
00:30:51,400 --> 00:30:52,560
will be announced.

372
00:30:53,840 --> 00:30:54,920
You're the Empress.

373
00:30:55,680 --> 00:30:56,920
You will be buried with him.

374
00:30:58,520 --> 00:30:59,920
But before that,

375
00:31:01,080 --> 00:31:04,400
I want you to eat well and stay alive.

376
00:31:05,600 --> 00:31:08,600
I want you to live in torment

377
00:31:09,360 --> 00:31:10,960
for every single moment.

378
00:31:57,600 --> 00:31:59,120
You know you're going to die,

379
00:31:59,640 --> 00:32:00,960
yet you don't even flinch.

380
00:32:03,160 --> 00:32:05,520
Truly a lovely couple
who would die for each other.

381
00:32:10,840 --> 00:32:13,080
He said he wanted to die with dignity.

382
00:32:14,720 --> 00:32:15,840
Then he turned around

383
00:32:16,360 --> 00:32:17,880
and jumped off Phoenix Terrace.

384
00:32:22,400 --> 00:32:24,680
He just wanted to be
thought dead and gone!

385
00:32:27,560 --> 00:32:29,040
How I wish

386
00:32:29,120 --> 00:32:30,720
I could run a sword
through his heart myself.

387
00:32:42,880 --> 00:32:44,080
Your Highness.

388
00:33:23,520 --> 00:33:24,920
He said he chose death,

389
00:33:25,720 --> 00:33:27,440
but jumped from Phoenix Terrace

390
00:33:29,280 --> 00:33:30,400
and disappeared.

391
00:33:30,480 --> 00:33:31,560
That means

392
00:33:34,040 --> 00:33:35,440
there's still hope.

393
00:33:50,080 --> 00:33:51,200
If he only disappeared,

394
00:33:52,160 --> 00:33:53,960
then there's still hope.

395
00:33:57,920 --> 00:34:02,880
THE START OF A BRIGHT FUTURE

396
00:34:29,639 --> 00:34:31,199
I passed by

397
00:34:31,280 --> 00:34:33,080
your favorite dessert shop today.

398
00:34:33,800 --> 00:34:35,280
I bought a few bowls

399
00:34:36,000 --> 00:34:38,120
of your favorites.

400
00:35:07,680 --> 00:35:08,680
Eat.

401
00:35:10,480 --> 00:35:12,840
Do you know why I like that shop?

402
00:35:15,040 --> 00:35:16,200
No.

403
00:35:17,800 --> 00:35:19,640
Because they use more sugar.

404
00:35:20,800 --> 00:35:21,800
When it's sweet,

405
00:35:23,640 --> 00:35:25,440
life doesn't feel so bitter.

406
00:35:55,000 --> 00:35:56,840
But now it feels too sweet.

407
00:35:57,720 --> 00:35:59,320
It doesn't taste good.

408
00:36:05,360 --> 00:36:06,640
Fine.

409
00:36:06,720 --> 00:36:08,000
Tomorrow I'll buy from another shop…

410
00:36:08,080 --> 00:36:09,880
Do you find this fun?

411
00:36:12,520 --> 00:36:13,640
How many days can you keep me here?

412
00:36:16,960 --> 00:36:18,440
I do find it fun.

413
00:36:19,760 --> 00:36:21,520
I think you're doing well here.

414
00:36:23,000 --> 00:36:24,560
Are you really that eager to leave me?

415
00:36:26,880 --> 00:36:28,560
Xiao Qianqing,

416
00:36:28,640 --> 00:36:30,280
I have to go.

417
00:36:32,160 --> 00:36:33,280
I need to save Cangcang.

418
00:37:04,360 --> 00:37:05,520
<i>What did you say?</i>

419
00:37:06,440 --> 00:37:08,000
She's started eating again?

420
00:37:08,080 --> 00:37:09,240
Yes, Madam.

421
00:37:09,960 --> 00:37:12,480
Her Majesty has found her will to live.

422
00:37:19,040 --> 00:37:22,840
I thought your love for Xiao Huan
was so deep

423
00:37:23,800 --> 00:37:26,560
that you'd cry day and night
and suffer endlessly.

424
00:37:33,640 --> 00:37:35,000
Since that's the case,

425
00:37:35,640 --> 00:37:37,120
I won't let you live

426
00:37:38,560 --> 00:37:40,520
a day longer.

427
00:37:55,840 --> 00:37:57,400
Your Majesty, be on your way, please.

428
00:37:59,400 --> 00:38:00,560
What?

429
00:38:01,640 --> 00:38:03,720
Du Tingxin can't wait

430
00:38:03,800 --> 00:38:05,080
for the Empress of Great Qi to be buried?

431
00:38:06,720 --> 00:38:07,920
Is she so afraid I'll live another day?

432
00:38:08,600 --> 00:38:12,080
Please do it yourself, Your Majesty.

433
00:38:12,160 --> 00:38:13,800
If I do it,

434
00:38:14,400 --> 00:38:16,680
it'll be painful.

435
00:38:16,760 --> 00:38:19,880
How could I give you what you want?

436
00:38:20,560 --> 00:38:21,920
Forgive me then.

437
00:38:48,640 --> 00:38:49,920
Zhong Lin?

438
00:38:55,720 --> 00:38:56,760
Let's go.

439
00:38:57,520 --> 00:38:58,600
Careful.

440
00:39:34,040 --> 00:39:34,920
Madam,

441
00:39:35,000 --> 00:39:37,120
Her Majesty has escaped.

442
00:39:38,400 --> 00:39:41,640
I didn't know
Her Majesty still had influence

443
00:39:41,720 --> 00:39:43,040
inside the palace.

444
00:39:46,480 --> 00:39:47,840
I truly

445
00:39:49,280 --> 00:39:51,080
underestimated her.

446
00:39:51,840 --> 00:39:56,600
FAYUN TEMPLE

447
00:40:04,840 --> 00:40:05,880
Father.

448
00:40:30,360 --> 00:40:31,360
Father.

449
00:40:34,160 --> 00:40:35,240
I'm here.

450
00:40:42,200 --> 00:40:43,800
Great that you're safe.

451
00:41:06,560 --> 00:41:07,600
Father.

452
00:41:10,000 --> 00:41:11,960
About what Du Tingxin has done,

453
00:41:13,200 --> 00:41:15,080
were you involved?

454
00:41:16,400 --> 00:41:17,800
Is it nippy outside?

455
00:41:20,200 --> 00:41:21,440
Your hands are cold.

456
00:41:21,520 --> 00:41:22,360
You're a grown-up

457
00:41:22,440 --> 00:41:23,960
and still don't know
how to take care of yourself.

458
00:41:24,760 --> 00:41:26,320
Here. Take this.

459
00:41:27,640 --> 00:41:28,800
Take this.

460
00:41:29,480 --> 00:41:31,240
Do you know about the death

461
00:41:33,120 --> 00:41:34,000
of the Empress Dowager Liu
and Princess Ying?

462
00:41:36,600 --> 00:41:37,720
Cangcang,

463
00:41:38,240 --> 00:41:40,280
you came here

464
00:41:40,800 --> 00:41:42,200
just to ask about this?

465
00:41:43,360 --> 00:41:44,360
Stop hiding it, Father.

466
00:41:45,320 --> 00:41:47,040
Xiao Huan has disappeared now.

467
00:41:47,560 --> 00:41:50,320
The Prince of
Yuzhang has turned against him

468
00:41:50,400 --> 00:41:52,960
and joined Du Tingxin in the coup.

469
00:41:53,480 --> 00:41:57,240
- I need to know the truth.
- Cangcang, stop digging.

470
00:41:57,320 --> 00:41:59,440
What matters most
now is that you head north

471
00:41:59,520 --> 00:42:00,840
and meet Jueding.

472
00:42:00,920 --> 00:42:03,640
The Northern Garrison Army
can protect you, understand?

473
00:42:03,720 --> 00:42:05,080
You want me

474
00:42:06,040 --> 00:42:07,040
to leave the Capital

475
00:42:08,600 --> 00:42:09,920
and go to the northern border?

476
00:42:13,160 --> 00:42:16,120
What about Xiao Huan? What about Great Qi?

477
00:42:16,200 --> 00:42:18,400
Cangcang, even if you find out the truth,

478
00:42:18,480 --> 00:42:19,800
what difference does it make?

479
00:42:19,880 --> 00:42:21,040
It does make a difference.

480
00:42:22,000 --> 00:42:23,040
Father,

481
00:42:23,120 --> 00:42:26,680
if Xiao Huan has only
disappeared, it means there's still hope.

482
00:42:26,760 --> 00:42:28,000
I believe

483
00:42:28,080 --> 00:42:29,880
he'll come back alive.

484
00:42:30,480 --> 00:42:32,240
That's why the truth matters.

485
00:42:32,960 --> 00:42:34,200
Father,

486
00:42:34,280 --> 00:42:35,560
please tell me.

487
00:42:36,800 --> 00:42:37,920
Cangcang,

488
00:42:39,000 --> 00:42:40,320
you're so stubborn.

489
00:42:41,800 --> 00:42:44,960
You wouldn't listen to
a single word I said.

490
00:42:49,280 --> 00:42:50,600
Do you know

491
00:42:51,640 --> 00:42:53,880
what you're about to face?

492
00:42:55,040 --> 00:42:57,080
Du Tingxin.

493
00:42:57,160 --> 00:42:59,160
She's a mad dog.
